{"id": "1270604062840324116", "channel_id": "1270604062840324116", "type": 0, "author_id": "299947644208414720", "author_name": "cs001092", "author_bot": false, "content": "终于打到375了1\n我是54321反着打\n第5关，第一次打，感觉能强杀精英不用用绕路，就重开一把\n造物够胡，没爪未必打得爆的了。镜像，相机和火柴盒也帮了不少\n不然血卖不够多也会悲剧\n\n第4关，镜像到偷力或许容易一点（鲨鱼启度得够）\n\n第3关，如果借泥工的24或许容易点，不过我已经用在第5关了。。。\n\n第2关，好在boss没有叠力，血回快，基本是能挺过去的\n\n第1关，之前打350的时候感觉回血够快，感觉能直接开局就开王，加上这轮融灾4关打完留了些回血命轮，就直接上了（混沌开局银造物也一定程度上帮了不少）", "timestamp": "2024-08-07T04:46:55.263000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1270604063355961375", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120512_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 181858, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604063355961375/Screenshot_20240807_120512_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfa7f&is=69caa8ff&hm=fc0e99669338032d8ebdd609a21f275f6b855489ec4772300d9819ae082a5f48&"}, {"id": "1270604063805014147", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120501_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183137, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604063805014147/Screenshot_20240807_120501_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfa7f&is=69caa8ff&hm=2127146b1c0e79d88dfad71298a5ede83487da6a264a3aedf52289519b5ee627&"}, {"id": "1270604064165593150", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120448_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 183637, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/1270604064165593150/Screenshot_20240807_120448_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg?ex=69cbfa7f&is=69caa8ff&hm=2f93164bca88a1018d4706aa63e856fb2916c9b42f8f06645f0255b6e906b4de&"}, {"id": "1270604064543211520", "filename": "Screenshot_20240807_120435_com.qookkagames.z1.gp.hk.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 193532, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1270604062840324116/12